                  $\sim 5$ pixels correlated
                  </p>
                <img src="matern_matrix.png"/>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="fragment" data-fragment-index="1">
            This covariance matrix accounts for the correlated structure of the residuals we saw earlier.
            </p>
    </section>
